author: Doug Ferguson, Ap Golf Writer
title: Steele takes 2-shot lead into weekend at Silverado
text: Photo: Eric Risberg, AP Brendan Steele putts on the second green of the Silverado Resort North Course during the second round of the Frys.com PGA Tour golf tournament Friday, Oct. 16, 2015, in Napa, Calif. Brendan Steele putts on the second green of the Silverado Resort... NAPA, Calif. (AP) — During his three-week offseason, Brendan Steele spent more time playing golf than practicing. That included some casual rounds with his buddies in which Steele was the one reaching of his wallet.
